# grove-testbench repo manifest
# One large, popular, grammar-backed codebase per language.
# Columns (whitespace-separated):  name  lang  url  sha
# Pinned to explicit SHAs for byte-reproducible images. Clone strategy:
#   git init <name> && cd <name>
#   git remote add origin <url>
#   git fetch --depth 1 origin <sha>
#   git checkout FETCH_HEAD
# (GitHub serves arbitrary reachable commits, so depth-1 fetch-by-sha works.)
# Pins resolved 2026-06-22 from each repo's default-branch HEAD.

